      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project or parts car. The exterior shows significant signs of age, including widespread paint oxidation, several noticeable dents, and areas of surface rust along the wheel arches. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and several interior trim pieces are loose or missing. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention; it currently runs but suffers from a rough idle and a noticeable leak in the exhaust system. It is being sold strictly 'as-is,' and we encourage any potential buyer to inspect it thoroughly before purchase.",
